body.name: ONPNO Reclining Office Chair with Massage, Ergonomic Office Chair w/Foot Rest, PU Leather Executive Computer Chair w/Heated, Padded Armrest, High Back Swivel Recliner for Office Home Study (Pink)
features: ✅【Ergonomic Desgin】- The Ergonomic office chair is made of faux leather, coming with double layer soft cushion can keep you away from the numbness caused by long hours sitting. Thickened headrest, Padded armrests and High backrest fit to the curve of human spine can give you strong support and help you release back & arm pressure.

✅【Adjustable Executive Chair】- Adjusting your backrest from 90°- 135°， you may easily adjust your backrest to your favorite position, the seat height adjusts from 22"- 26" for you to adjust to the ideal height. Retractable footrest allows you to relax during a busy workday. The chair easily swivels 360 degrees to get the maximum use of your workspace without strain.

✅【5-Mode Massage Function】- You can freely choose your favorite modes of vibration massage by pressing one remote control. 5-mode of massage, 6 massage points, changing intensity between high and low, you can set up your timer preference from 15/60 mins. After a long day, you can relax in a reclining office chair.

✅【SMOOTH ROLLING & STURDY BASE】 - Class-A durable nylon office chair caster wheels roll easily. Smooth-rolling office desk chair on any kind of floor. Passed BIFMA 200,000 rolling test. BIFMA, SGS explosion-proof gas and heavy metal five-legged base for heavy duty office chair. weight capacity of up to 330 lbs.

✅【INSTALLATION & WARRANTY】- We have detailed installation instructions and presented the necessary installation tools, enable everyone to quickly assemble into a office chair. Estimated assembly time in about 10-30mins. We provide 360 days warranty. Please feel free to contact us if you meet any product issues, service team will reply you within 24 hours.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 18, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I absolutely love this chair. It was easy to assemble. The color is as depicted on Amazon. It’s comfortable and I love the massager.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 22, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I was so excited about this chair but the wheels fell off after a week and 3 weeks later one of the arms broke off. The company replaced the wheels and the arm and gave mea $30 refund but I’d rather have a sturdy reliable chair! And if you are in it for a full work day, get a cushion because the seat is NOT well padded. Fortunately MY SEAT is lol

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 17, 2022
reviews.reviewText: Chair is great I’ve had it for ~10 days at this point and it works well. Instructions are straightforward with pictures (I’ve put together an office chair before). The lumbar support is small and low so I’ve added my own pillow for more support. The chair takes some “breaking in”, I also added a pillow for my tailbone for sitting for long periods because (just like any chair) it comes out the box a little “stiff”. The massaging is largely a strong vibration vs rollers like other massage chairs and I haven’t used the heated feature as it’s still quite warm out. Overall, it works as intended.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Pink and perfect
reviews.reviewText: I absolutely LOVE,LOVE MY NEW PINK BABY! I am over the moon and the features are the best,massage and heat. I have had 3 car accidents and I needed this chair, it provides deep massage and comfortable heat with different modes and levels for your entire back. Only think Iam almost 6 feet, the foot rest is a bit too short for me. But overall Ism comfortable for my size, Iam 267lbs easy, good fit. The color is amazing, and the feel of real leather great. As you can see I'm impressed, recommended to purchase 👌

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Shipping was fast. I don’t recommend going with a light color it will stain pretty quickly and look old. I sat with dark jeans and the chair stained and won’t come off ( I purchased the off white/cream color one). The massage feature is more like a vibration and very minimal. I was disappointed. The cushion is also very minimal after a month or two it feels like you are sitting on a plank of wood. You will need to get some cushion to put on top. I personally do not recommend this chair. The price is good but the chair is not of good quality. I would recommend to invest a bit more and get a good quality chair if you are someone like me who works from home and spends 8 hrs a day on it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Chair for very short people
reviews.reviewText: Negatives: chair has one setting- very low to the ground, so you are like me 5’8 you will have to squat before seating down. The chair is not sturdy and the click-clack mechanism that keeps the main cylinder and base/ legs together is cheap and weak.Positive: easy to assembly, even though the assembly instructions are not smart.I would NOT recommend this chair for someone who is over 5’7 or 150 pounds!
